    {"id":"post_1","type":"sharp_opinion","source_theme":"one_up_authority","text":"Asking an owner what they want in a property manager outsources the diagnosis to the least informed person in the room.","engagement_prompt":false,"post_role":"sharpest_observation","best_timing":"early_week","publish_after_linkedin":false,"source_trace":{"book_slug":"elite_sales_strategies","source_file":"linkedin/post_1.txt","theme":"one_up_authority","related_linkedin_post":"linkedin/post_1.txt"}},
    {"id":"post_2","type":"recognition","source_theme":"information_disparity","text":"Commission pressure often starts because the VRM acted like a waiter taking an order instead of the operator with the actual market data.","engagement_prompt":false,"post_role":"recognition_line","best_timing":"mid_week","publish_after_linkedin":true,"source_trace":{"book_slug":"elite_sales_strategies","source_file":"linkedin/post_2.txt","theme":"information_disparity","related_linkedin_post":"linkedin/post_2.txt"}},
    {"id":"post_3","type":"recognition","source_theme":"sense_maker_role","text":"Owners don't need more STR data. They need someone to explain which numbers matter and which ones are market noise.","engagement_prompt":false,"post_role":"recognition_line","best_timing":"mid_week","publish_after_linkedin":true,"source_trace":{"book_slug":"elite_sales_strategies","source_file":"linkedin/post_3.txt","theme":"sense_maker_role","related_linkedin_post":"linkedin/post_3.txt"}},
    {"id":"post_4","type":"diagnostic","source_theme":"guide_not_grader","text":"Useful self-check before a listing appointment: am I showing up to guide this owner to a better decision, or to validate whatever assumption makes the deal easier to close?","engagement_prompt":false,"post_role":"tactical_question","best_timing":"after_post_1","publish_after_linkedin":true,"source_trace":{"book_slug":"elite_sales_strategies","source_file":"newsletter/newsletter.txt","theme":"guide_not_grader","related_linkedin_post":"linkedin/post_2.txt"}},
    {"id":"post_5","type":"story_detail","source_theme":"correcting_bad_data","text":"One of the more valuable things a VRM can say is: 'Let me make sure we're working from the real number, not the exciting number.' Not flashy. Very differentiating.","engagement_prompt":false,"post_role":"story_detail","best_timing":"mid_week","publish_after_linkedin":true,"source_trace":{"book_slug":"elite_sales_strategies","source_file":"newsletter/newsletter.txt","theme":"correcting_bad_data","related_linkedin_post":"linkedin/post_2.txt"}},
    {"id":"post_6","type":"engagement","source_theme":"owner_self_diagnosis","text":"Are you seeing more owners come in anchored to the wrong metric right now: management fee, upside projection, or whatever AirDNA screenshot made their week?","engagement_prompt":true,"post_role":"conversation_opener","best_timing":"late_week","publish_after_linkedin":true,"source_trace":{"book_slug":"elite_sales_strategies","source_file":"newsletter/newsletter.txt","theme":"owner_self_diagnosis","related_linkedin_post":"linkedin/post_1.txt"}},
    {"id":"post_7","type":"author_engagement","source_theme":"author_application","text":"Applying Anthony Iannarino's One-Up and Sense-Maker ideas to VRM has made it clear that owners rarely need another friendly pitch. They need a clearer map.","engagement_prompt":false,"post_role":"author_engagement","best_timing":"after_series_launch","publish_after_linkedin":true,"source_trace":{"book_slug":"elite_sales_strategies","source_file":"newsletter/newsletter.txt","theme":"author_application","related_linkedin_post":"linkedin/post_3.txt"}}
